cu.explanation_en: Setting the MAC log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and prevent proper MAC layer log output.

du.explanation_en: Setting the do CSIRS to an out-of-range value of 3 will cause CSI-RS configuration errors and prevent proper channel state information reference signal transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將 do CSIRS 設定為超出範圍的值 3，會導致 CSI-RS 配置錯誤，並阻止正確的通道狀態資訊參考信號傳輸。
